Package: Time.R
Title: Estimates Time of Concentration and Lag Time for Watersheds
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2026-05-27
Authors@R: person("Alonso", "Arriagada", email = "alonso.arriagada@usach.cl",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Functions to estimate the time of concentration
    and lag times for watersheds based on their morphometric characteristics.
    It includes various methods for calculation and offers plotting functionalities
    for comparative analysis.
